      "title": "3-hour power cut approved for tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) today approved a three-hour power cut for tomorrow.",
        "Accordingly, the areas under groups A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, P, Q, R, S, T, U, V and W will have one hour and 40 minutes during the daytime and one hour and 20 minutes during the night.",
        "The areas under the group CC\u00a0 will impose two hour and 30 minutes from 6.00a.m to 8.30a.m and areas under the groups M, N, O, X, Y and Z will imposer three hours from 5.30am to 8.30am. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
